      <title>Charter要求客户在云DVR出现故障后删除视频</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/charter-asks-customers-to-delete-videos-amid-cloud-dvr-glitches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Charter Communications Inc.表示，由于最近推出的流媒体服务无法预见的需求，该公司的在线视频存储功能一直步履蹒跚。它敦促客户在解决问题时删除旧的或不需要的录音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/charter-asks-customers-to-delete-videos-amid-cloud-dvr-glitches</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微因盈利担忧而跌至近两个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/super-micro-drops-near-two-month-low-on-earnings-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[服务器制造商超微电脑公司(Super Micro Computer Inc.)公布了第三季度业绩的日期，但没有预先公布业绩，该公司股价周五出现约两个月来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/super-micro-drops-near-two-month-low-on-earnings-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2026 年，挪威的电动汽车可能会超越柴油车竞争对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/electric-cars-in-norway-may-push-diesel-rivals-off-top-by-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威是放弃内燃机汽车的先驱，到 2026 年，电动汽车可能会成为最大的乘用车类别，到 2030 年，电动汽车将占所有汽车的一半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/electric-cars-in-norway-may-push-diesel-rivals-off-top-by-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔塔正在洽谈最快 5 月收购和硕 iPhone 业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tata-in-talks-to-acquire-pegatron-s-iphone-operations-as-soon-as-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔塔集团可能最早于 5 月份达成协议，控制和硕在印度的 iPhone 制造业务，从而巩固苹果公司与印度最具影响力的企业集团之一的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tata-in-talks-to-acquire-pegatron-s-iphone-operations-as-soon-as-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Telegram 消息服务允许 Tether 稳定币支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/telegram-messaging-service-to-allow-tether-stablecoin-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tether 是世界上最常用的稳定币发行商，它与 TON 基金会合作，允许客户使用流行的 Telegram 加密即时通讯服务发送加密货币支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/telegram-messaging-service-to-allow-tether-stablecoin-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州小城击退了与俄罗斯有关的黑客对供水系统的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tiny-texas-city-repels-russia-tied-hackers-eyeing-water-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当迈克·赛珀特 (Mike Cypert) 接到电话称德克萨斯州偏远社区的公用事业遭到黑客攻击时，他跑过办公室拔掉了运行该市供水系统的计算机的电源插头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tiny-texas-city-repels-russia-tied-hackers-eyeing-water-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 11:35:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着用户涌向昂贵的高级卡，美国运通收入猛增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/amex-revenue-jumps-as-consumers-flock-to-pricey-premium-cards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国运通公司报告称，由于消费者继续涌向该公司的优质信用卡产品，今年前三个月的收入超出了预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/amex-revenue-jumps-as-consumers-flock-to-pricey-premium-cards</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 11:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施耐德与美国软件制造商宾利进行交易谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/schneider-electric-says-it-s-holding-talks-with-bentley-systems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[施耐德电气正在与工程软件制造商 Bentley Systems Inc. 就一项潜在交易进行谈判，这可能为法国企业对美国公司的最大收购之一铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/schneider-electric-says-it-s-holding-talks-with-bentley-systems</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 06:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix 因预测疲弱而下跌，并计划结束订阅人数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/netflix-adds-9-33-million-customers-crushing-street-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，Netflix Inc. 股价创下九个月来最大跌幅，原因是营收预测疲软，并且警告这家流媒体巨头将在 2025 年停止报告用户数量，这给今年原本强劲的开局蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/netflix-adds-9-33-million-customers-crushing-street-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 首次推出 Llama 3，这是为聊天机器人提供动力的最新 AI 模型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/meta-debuts-llama-3-latest-ai-model-for-training-chatbots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms Inc. 推出了强大的 Llama 人工智能模型的新版本，这是其为跟上 OpenAI 和 Alphabet Inc. 旗下谷歌等公司类似技术的步伐而做出的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/meta-debuts-llama-3-latest-ai-model-for-training-chatbots</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
